               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18410301-name-413" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18410301-name-413" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18410301-name-413" type="surname" value="GOULD"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18410301-name-413" type="given" value="CHARLES"></interp>CHARLES GOULD</persName>
                  </hi>. I am in the employ of Michael Hall and another, linen-drapers, in St. Pauls-churchyard. On the 20th of February, the prisoner came for a pair of braces for 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>., and while the young man went to another part of the shop, he took five handkerchiefs in one piece, and put them under his jacket—I took them from him, and sent for a police<lb></lb>man.</p>
