                        <interp inst="t18410301-name-414" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>THOMAS WALKER</persName>
                  </hi>. I was in the shop—the prisoner came in, and asked me for a pair of braces about 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.—I went to get them, and when I returned, he was in custody of Gould, and was begging for mercy—these are the handkerchiefs.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner.</hi> The handkerchiefs were on the counter—I laid hold of one to look at—I only had them in my hand.</p>
